    <item>
      <title>Open Source Camp</title>
      <link>https://localhost/030_news/2021/2021-11-23-Open-Source-Camp.html</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Nov 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">030_news/2021/2021-11-23-Open-Source-Camp.html</guid>
      <description>
      &lt;div id=&quot;toc&quot; class=&quot;toc&quot;&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;toctitle&quot;&gt;Table of Contents&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;sectlevel1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#_open_source_camp&quot;&gt;Open Source Camp&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;!-- endtoc --&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;sect1&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;_open_source_camp&quot;&gt;Open Source Camp&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;sectionbody&quot;&gt;
&lt;style&gt;
.center {
  text-align: center;
}
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;imageblock center&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;
&lt;img src=&quot;https://cyberland.ijug.eu/assets/logo/camp-logo.png&quot; alt=&quot;camp logo&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The next &lt;a href=&quot;https://cyberland.ijug.eu/2021-12-open-source-camp/&quot;&gt;Cyberland Open Source Camp&lt;/a&gt; is just around the corner.
This time, &lt;a href=&quot;https://doctoolchain.org&quot;&gt;docToolchain&lt;/a&gt; will be one of the featured open source projects for this event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So, let&amp;#8217;s be prepared and think about what are realistic tasks which we could solve during those few ours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here are some handpicked issues from the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/docToolchain/docToolchain/issues&quot;&gt;list of open issues&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ulist&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/docToolchain/docToolchain/issues/578&quot;&gt;Autocompletion for the CLI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/docToolchain/docToolchain/issues/692&quot;&gt;generateSite: additional navigation level on the left&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/docToolchain/docToolchain/issues/699&quot;&gt;create multi-branch github pages example&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/docToolchain/docToolchain/issues/679&quot;&gt;Investigations with Gitpod?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or even create a new &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/docToolchain/docToolchain/issues/700&quot;&gt;InitRepo task&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have your own idea, &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:ralf.d.mueller@gmail.com&quot;&gt;please let me know&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To vote for a task, please &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/docToolchain/docToolchain/issues?q=is%3Aopen+label%3AHackergarten+sort%3Areactions-heart-desc&quot;&gt;go to github&lt;/a&gt; and add a ❤️ reaction to the issue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
	  </description>
    </item>
    
