&lt;i class=&quot;fa icon-important&quot; title=&quot;Important&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;
Thanx to all contributors, sponsors, and users of docToolchain for your efforts!
Without you, this project would not exist 💯
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy writing!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ralf&lt;/p&gt;
